item.title: days #26-#30
item.description: this week has been busy & full of life lessons. i’ve traveled to & from tucson (soon to be to & from again), assisted bob in editing our film to submit to a film festival, attempted to actually get some work done at the office, and engaged in a work activity that involved downtown PHX & the light rail. that last one is what i want to really examine right now.
